Maneuver Mastery (Steal)		KEY:Maneuver Mastery Steal ~ Magus Arcana		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.MagusArcana																												DESC:You have mastered the steal combat maneuver. Whenever you attempt a steal combat maneuver, you use your magus level in place of your base attack bonus (in addition to any base attack bonus gained from other classes).																																																																																										BONUS:VAR|CMB_Steal|MagusArcanaLVL-floor(var("CL=Magus")*3/4)																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.12
