#Block: Swamp Domain
Natural Healing			KEY:Natural Healing ~ Swamp Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower.CheckList			DEFINE:NaturalHealingTimes|DomainSwampTimes+CHA-WIS												DESC:You can channel energy (as a cleric of your druid level) a %1 times per day, but only to heal animals, plants, and vermin. You may reduce the number of dice healed to cure ability damage (your choice) to all affected creatures, curing 1 point of ability damage for each d6 that the channel energy is reduced. You can take other feats to add to this ability, such as Extra Channel, but not feats that alter this ability, such as Elemental Channel and Alignment Channel.|NaturalHealingTimes																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.35	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|NaturalHealingTimes	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per Day
