Mantle against Chaos	KEY:Mantle against Chaos ~ Order Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike			DEFINE:MantleAgainstChaosTimes|DomainOrderLVL																								DESC:You can use protection from chaos on yourself or another creature as a spell-like ability. You can use this ability %1 minutes per day. This duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be used in 1 minute increments.|MantleAgainstChaosTimes																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.43
Commanding Order		KEY:Commanding Order ~ Order Domain			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.SpellLike			DEFINE:CommandingOrderDC|DomainOrderDC																									DESC:You can use greater command (DC %2), except it only affects a single target.  You can use this ability %1 times per day.|DomainOrderTimes|CommandingOrderDC																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|CommandingOrderDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Commanding Order)										SOURCEPAGE:p.43

