Relentless Footing	KEY:Relentless Footing ~ Persistence Domain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																	DESC:As a swift action, you can add 10 feet to your land speed. This increase counts as an enhancement bonus, and it affects your jumping distance as normal for increased speed. You can use this ability %1 times per day.|DomainPersistenceTimes																																																																																					BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE.Walk|10|TYPE=Enhancement|PREAPPLY:PC																															SOURCEPAGE:p.43
Inner Strength		KEY:Inner Strength ~ Persistence Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural		DEFINE:InnerStrengthDice|DomainPersistenceLVL/2																								DESC:Once per day, you may heal yourself as a swift action, healing %1d6 hit points. When you use this ability, you can also remove one of the following conditions from yourself: blinded, confused, dazzled, deafened, frightened, nauseated, shaken, sickened, or staggered.|InnerStrengthDice																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.43

#Block: Tactics Inquisition
Inquisitor's Direction	KEY:Inquisitor's Direction ~ Tactics Domain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																	DESC:At the start of your turn, you can choose to enter a tranquil, reflective state and forgo all actions (standard, move, swift, immediate, and free actions, including attacks of opportunity) for that round; one ally of your choice within 30 feet gains the benefit of haste for 1 round. You can use this ability %1 times per day.|DomainTacticsTimes																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.43
Grant the Initiative	KEY:Grant the Initiative ~ Tactics Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura	DEFINE:GrantTheInitiativeBonus|WIS																										DESC:You and all allies within 30 feet may add +%1 to your initiative checks.|GrantTheInitiativeBonus																																																																																																		BONUS:COMBAT|INITIATIVE|GrantTheInitiativeBonus|PREAPPLY:ANYPC																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.44

#Block: Torture Inquisition
Torturer's Presence	KEY:Torturer's Presence ~ Torture Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																	DESC:You gain a +2 bonus when using the Intimidate skill.  This is in addition to your bonus for Stern Gaze.																																																																																																																					BONUS:SKILL|Intimidate|2																										SOURCEPAGE:p.44
Torturer's Touch		KEY:Torturer's Touch ~ Torture Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.SpellLike																																		DESC:You may use touch of fatigue as a spell-like ability.  Creatures that are immune to pain effects are immune to this touch.  You can use this ability %1 times per day.|DomainTortureTimes																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.44
Critical Precision	KEY:Critical Precision ~ Torture Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																	DESC:When you roll a critical threat, you may expend one use of your torturer's touch ability to add +4 on your critical confirmation roll. This does not stack with Critical Focus.																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.44

