# Ability Name		Unique Key				Category of Ability		Type								Visible	Required Ability								Multiple Requirements																		Define							Description																																																																																																																		Bonus to Ability Pool	Combat bonus						Add to base move			Modify VAR								Cost		Apply Kit				Source Page
