Final Revelation					KEY:Final Revelation ~ Time Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.FinalTimeRevelation																																																	SPELLS:Innate|TIMES=1|Time Stop								DESC:You become a true master of time.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:You become a true master of time and stop aging. You cannot be magically aged and no longer take penalties to your ability scores for aging. Age bonuses still accrue, and any aging penalties that you have already accrued remain in place. You cannot die of old age, but you can be killed or die through accident, disease, poison, or other external effects. In addition, you can cast time stop once per day as a spell-like ability.

#Block: Oracle Revelations: Wood
Bend the Grain					KEY:Bend the Grain ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:BendTheGrainTimes|1+min(2,classlevel("Oracle")/7)																																									DESC:You can shape or warp wooden objects.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:As a standard action, %1/day, you can shape or warp wooden objects. This functions as either wood shape or warp wood.|BendTheGrainTimes	BENEFIT:You can use this ability to push wood away from you, as repel wood.|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11
Lignification					KEY:Lignification ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.WoodRevelation.RevelationTargetOneOnly			PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11	DEFINE:LignificationTimes|1	DEFINE:LignificationDC|10+classlevel("Oracle")/2+CHA	DEFINE:LignificationDuration|classlevel("Oracle")/2																												DESC:You can turn a creature into wood.																																																																																																																																																																																											BONUS:VAR|LignificationTimes|1|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=15																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:You can turn a creature into wood %1/day. As a standard action, you may direct your gaze against a single creature within 30 feet. The targeted creature (along with all its carried gear) must make a Fortitude save (DC %2) or turn into a mindless, inert statue made out of wood for %3 rounds. This ability otherwise functions as a flesh to stone spell, except the target turns to wood instead of stone. This can be reversed by any effect that can reverse flesh to stone.|LignificationTimes|LignificationDC|LignificationDuration
Speak with Wood					KEY:Speak with Wood ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation							PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11	DEFINE:SpeakWithWoodDuration|classlevel("Oracle")																																										DESC:You can talk to wood and learn what it knows.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:You can talk to wood and learn what it knows. You must spend 1 minute meditating on and communing with the wood. At the end of this time, you can speak with the wood. This functions as the stone tell spell, except with wood instead of stones. You can use this ability for %1 minutes. This duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be used in 1-minute increments. You can speak with natural or worked wood.|SpeakWithWoodDuration
Thorn Burst						KEY:Thorn Burst ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:ThornBurstDice|max(1,classlevel("Oracle")/2)	DEFINE:ThornBurstDC|10+classlevel("Oracle")/2+CHA	DEFINE:ThornBurstTimes|1+classlevel("Oracle")/5																									DESC:You can cause sharp splinters of wood to explode outward from your body.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:As a swift action, you can cause sharp splinters of wood to explode outward from your body. These splinters deal %1d6 points of piercing damage to all creatures within a 10-foot burst. A Reflex save (DC %2) halves this damage. In addition, the sharp splinters count as caltrops (see page 155 of the Core Rulebook) in the area until your next turn. You can use this ability %3/day.|ThornBurstDice|ThornBurstDC|ThornBurstTimes
Tree Form						KEY:Tree Form ~ Wood Mystery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation							PRECLASS:1,Oracle=3	DEFINE:TreeFormDuration|classlevel("Oracle")																																											DESC:You can assume the form of a plant.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:As a standard action, you can assume the following forms: a Large living or dead tree or shrub, as tree shape	BENEFIT:a Small or Medium plant creature, as plant shape I|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=9	BENEFIT:a Large plant creature, as plant shape II|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11	BENEFIT:a Huge plant creature, as plant shape III|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=13	BENEFIT:and you can use this ability once per day, but the duration is %1 hours.|TreeFormDuration
Wood Armor						KEY:Wood Armor ~ Wood Mystery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:WoodArmorBonus|4	DEFINE:WoodArmorDuration|classlevel("Oracle")																																							DESC:You can conjure wood armor around yourself.																																																																																																										BONUS:COMBAT|AC|WoodArmorBonus|TYPE=Armor|PREAPPLY:PC																																																																							BONUS:VAR|WoodArmorBonus|max(0,2*floor((classlevel("Oracle")-3)/4))																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:You can conjure wooden armor around yourself, which grants you a +%1 armor bonus.|WoodArmorBonus	BENEFIT:This armor grants you DR 5/slashing.|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=13	BENEFIT:You can use this armor for %1 hours per day. This duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be spent in 1-hour increments. The armor vanishes if you remove it.|WoodArmorDuration
Wood Bond						KEY:Wood Bond ~ Wood Mystery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:WoodBondBonus|1+classlevel("Oracle")/5																																											DESC:Your wooden weapons become an extension of your body.																																																																																																																																																																																																																						BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Wooden|TOHIT|WoodBondBonus|TYPE=Competence																		SOURCEPAGE:p.57	BENEFIT:Your mystical bond with wood is such that your weapons become an extension of your body. You gain a +%1 competence bonus on attack rolls when wielding a weapon made of or mostly consisting of wood (such as a bow, club, quarterstaff, or spear).|WoodBondBonus
Wood Sight						KEY:Wood Sight ~ Wood Mystery				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:WoodSightDistance|classlevel("Oracle")	DEFINE:WoodSightDuration|classlevel("Oracle")																																			DESC:You can alter your vision to see through plant growth.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.58	BENEFIT:As a move action, you can alter your vision to see through underbrush and plant growth that would normally grant concealment, up to a range of 60 feet (though darkness and other obstacles still may block your sight).	BENEFIT:You can use this ability to see through wood or other plant material as easily as if it were transparent glass, penetrating %1 feet of wood.|WoodSightDistance|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=7	BENEFIT:You can use this ability %1 rounds per day, but these rounds do not need to be consecutive.|WoodSightDuration
Wooden Weapon					KEY:Wooden Weapon ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation											DEFINE:WoodenWeaponDuration|classlevel("Oracle")	DEFINE:WoodenWeaponTimes|3+CHA	DEFINE:WoodenWeaponEnhancement|1																														DESC:You can create a wooden weapon.																																																																																																																																																																																											BONUS:VAR|WoodenWeaponEnhancement|1|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=15	BONUS:VAR|WoodenWeaponEnhancement|1|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=19																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.58	BENEFIT:You can create a wooden club, quarterstaff, longspear, shortspear, or spear that lasts for %1 minutes. This weapon is appropriate for your size. You are considered proficient with the weapon. The weapon disappears after 1 round if it leaves your grasp. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|WoodenWeaponDuration|WoodenWeaponTimes|!PRECLASS:1,Oracle=3	BENEFIT:You can create a masterwork wooden club, quarterstaff, longspear, shortspear, or spear that lasts for %1 minutes. This weapon is appropriate for your size. You are considered proficient with the weapon. The weapon disappears after 1 round if it leaves your grasp. You can use this ability %2 times per day.|WoodenWeaponDuration|WoodenWeaponTimes|PREMULT:2,[!PRECLASS:1,Oracle=7],[PRECLASS:1,Oracle=3]	BENEFIT:You can create a +%2 wooden club, quarterstaff, longspear, shortspear, or spear that lasts for %1 minutes. This weapon is appropriate for your size. You are considered proficient with the weapon. The weapon disappears after 1 round if it leaves your grasp. You can use this ability %3 times per day.|WoodenWeaponDuration|WoodenWeaponEnhancement|WoodenWeaponTimes|PREMULT:2,[!PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11],[PRECLASS:1,Oracle=7]	BENEFIT:You can create a +%2 keen (or equivalent increase to its critical threat range, if it is a bludgeoning weapon) wooden club, quarterstaff, longspear, shortspear, or spear that lasts for %1 minutes. This weapon is appropriate for your size. You are considered proficient with the weapon. The weapon disappears after 1 round if it leaves your grasp. You can use this ability %3 times per day.|WoodenWeaponDuration|WoodenWeaponEnhancement|WoodenWeaponTimes|PRECLASS:1,Oracle=11
Woodland Stride					KEY:Woodland Stride ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.WoodRevelation																																																													DESC:You can move through undergrowth at your normal speed.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.58	BENEFIT:You can move through any sort of undergrowth (such as natural thorns, briars, overgrown areas, and similar terrain) at your normal speed and without taking damage or suffering any other impairment. Thorns, briars, and overgrown areas that have been magically manipulated to impede motion, however, still affect you.
Final Revelation					KEY:Final Revelation ~ Wood Mystery			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.FinalWoodRevelation																																																														DESC:You become a living creature of wood.									TEMPLATE:Wood Mystery Final Revelation																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.58	BENEFIT:You become a living creature of wood. You are forevermore treated as the plant type rather than your original type for the purpose of spells and magical effects. Your skin takes on the appearance of polished wood grain, and you gain a +4 natural armor bonus to your Armor Class and damage reduction 10/- against wooden weapons or any natural attacks made by a wooden or woodlike creature. You gain immunity to paralysis, poison, polymorph, sleep, and stunning. At will, you can meld with any tree or single block of wood (as meld into stone, except wood only, and with no limit to how long you can remain in the wood).


